    public interface NamedEnum
extends Named
    A named enum instance.

    This extends Named for implementations of Enum. The name is provided by the Enum.toString() method of the enum, typically using the EnumNames helper class.

    Implementations must provide a static method of(String) that allows the instance to be created from the name, see Named.of(Class, String).
